    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I understand the caveat about systemic factors, but for the sake of a statistical breakdown, I need to look at the raw numbers. Could you provide more specific details on which ethnic groups are most frequently identified in these crime statistics? Also, if we're looking strictly at the data before adjusting for socioeconomic status, what kind of disproportionate trends are we seeing?",
